는 거짓이야!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">a_if는 True입니다.</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>한줄로 바꾸는 법</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"a_if는 True입니다.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> a_if <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"너는 거짓이야!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">a_if는 True입니다.</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">b_if <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> b_if <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"짱 크네\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">elif</span> b_if <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> b_if <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"애매하네\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">elif</span> b_if <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"작네\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"넌 뭐야?!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">애매하네</code></pre></div>","categories":["Python","기초"],"date":"October 12, 2023","description":"파이썬 기초","id":"7dfe38e4-12e6-5ea5-849d-4012772d9f59","keywords":["Python","기초","조건문"],"slug":"/my-first-article/python7/","title":"[파이썬 기초] 조건문","readingTime":{"text":"1 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}